{"data":[{"id":560978794,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"8c0b619de43f1583004c834d154cce33","url_token":"qian-feng-81-27","name":"深海逐豚","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5c2e7ca7afa7f98e4a848ec72964c5a0_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5c2e7ca7afa7f98e4a848ec72964c5a0_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/8c0b619de43f1583004c834d154cce33","user_type":"people","headline":"理想主义中的悲观生活者。","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560978794","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545903980,"updated_time":1545973098,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e谢邀。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果是我，看到题目，我会答题：略。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我觉得题主的问题应该表达错了，或者表达不清楚。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e应该是，一个高中生喜欢钻研数学问题，平时也很喜欢看其他大佬解题的思路，包括其他人证明猜想但不准确的过程，但其实自己是做不出来的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e突然有一天，碰巧证明了哥德巴赫猜想。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而让这位高中生完全重新做一次，他做不出来，他甚至无法完全回答提问者的问题，但他能拿出一个完全正确的解题方式。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e就像玄幻小说《大主宰》里，主角参加大千盟组织的大千会，在小世界里争夺功法和宝物，小世界里有邪魔，邪魔分为魔王，魔帝，天魔帝等。大千盟有一个规定，只要大千世界的人杀一个邪魔，就能给自己的身份牌加积分，而杀了天魔帝的人，就可以直接成为诛魔王。主角功力还不够，在最后时刻，让自己已经死去但镇压着天魔帝的祖先附体，最后终于打败了天魔帝，而主角想起大千会那个规定，跟祖先说，让自己用令牌收一丝天魔帝的魂试一下能不能成功，然后直接成为第二位诛魔王。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e第一位诛魔王是一个一个打上去的，段位为大千世界最高几人之一。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后的结果是，大千会承认了主角诛魔王的身份，但因为其本身能力的不足，大千盟无法为其提供其他实质性帮助，不会给主角提供药材，功法，仆人等等，只给了一个让别人不好明面动主角的名号。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以，你觉得呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e好吧，我只是不相信题主能证明而已。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而如果你真的证明出哥猜，北大清华不是保送，而是特邀。国外top大学也会争夺，因为你是数学界一颗闪闪发亮的新星。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e大佬，我等你论证过程。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560862048,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"67dd4e077493d74c5b5e2eb98341544f","url_token":"qi-heng-zhi-fu-35","name":"奇恒之腑","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/67dd4e077493d74c5b5e2eb98341544f","user_type":"people","headline":"懒癌患者","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560862048","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545894355,"updated_time":1545894355,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e希望题主成功之后不要忘记评论中对你表达善意的人，好好加油吧。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560479057,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560479057","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545841164,"updated_time":1545841175,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我竟然还看到有回答揪着那句1.1公布欢迎观看不放的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我作为一个数学从来没有及过格的文科生，虽然不懂你们在探讨什么高深的学术问题，但我不喜欢你们自以为是的幽默。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562780395,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"283181e11d19bcc34f2164cf7146adc6","url_token":"wu-guang-yue-8","name":"吴光越","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/283181e11d19bcc34f2164cf7146adc6","user_type":"people","headline":"数学家，物理学家，思想家","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562780395","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546145390,"updated_time":1546246098,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e题主你那么厉害来帮我解一个微分方程吧！也不难，求一个函数它的导函数加上二次导函数等于e的sinx次方这个函数就好！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e因为说真的，证明哥德巴赫猜想是真的不能保送的，不是不能保送清华北大，而是不能保送几乎任意一所大学。因为你的水平就只是那样，你证得出来只能说明哥德巴赫猜想简单而不能说明你厉害。嗯，就是这样。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e试问你除了哥德巴赫猜想还会证什么呢？那只是一个猜想啊！你既没有发明什么也没有创造什么更没有建立什么……就只是一个猜想啊！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e只是证明哥德巴赫猜想我也行啊！我定义满足它的数是大偶数就好了嘛！这样它不就成了吗？只是它只是一个不知道哪个宇宙中一个显而易见的事实而已。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以说，证明哥德巴赫猜想还不如来帮我解微分方程呢！我拿我四色定理的证明和你换任意微分方程的解法好不好？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e还是说你感兴趣的只是上清北，对证明一点都不在乎呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e最后大家也别喷了，喷之前先告诉我上面那个微分方程的解好不好？连个微分方程都不会解你好意思笑别人嘛！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560521514,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"718dcafaf7528e506e3e375d4bd32ff8","url_token":"bu-er-99-34","name":"不二","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-04afc7fc76e48f6fec3831cc6a6282fe_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-04afc7fc76e48f6fec3831cc6a6282fe_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/718dcafaf7528e506e3e375d4bd32ff8","user_type":"people","headline":"我看世界，世界看我","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560521514","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545847419,"updated_time":1545847419,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不管怎样，我还是希望各位不要谋杀了一个新的灵魂。笔下留情。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560061246,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"2b8fcf25adbe2959e1c08c6d12ceaced","url_token":"deng-xian-tao-78","name":"阳光月光","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f0830749792bae5adbd5e493d610e289_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f0830749792bae5adbd5e493d610e289_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/2b8fcf25adbe2959e1c08c6d12ceaced","user_type":"people","headline":"客观看待政治正确的价值观，远离道德武装者。","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560061246","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545805867,"updated_time":1545805867,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e如果一个对高等数学工具没有深刻体会的人(无论高中生还是本科生)证明出来了哥德巴赫猜想，那是对自欧拉以来的所有做数学的人的赤裸裸的侮辱，甚至是对人类文明和人类作为高等生物的整体智慧的侮辱。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560984431,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"9442ada98f9bf11c51cdb377880fa002","url_token":"li-deng-hui-27","name":"凛时雨","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-89c81e7e59b5e6f522a2c742cb53544c_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-89c81e7e59b5e6f522a2c742cb53544c_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/9442ada98f9bf11c51cdb377880fa002","user_type":"people","headline":"窃•格瓦拉真理贯彻者","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560984431","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545904496,"updated_time":1545904496,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e为什么这个问题还没有上热搜？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560128626,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"335f269651f65a8581f89af3918771bf","url_token":"cong-ming-xiao-ben-gou","name":"聪明小笨狗","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-c3179d804b873cc1d59204ab575afc21_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-c3179d804b873cc1d59204ab575afc21_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/335f269651f65a8581f89af3918771bf","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560128626","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545811580,"updated_time":1545811580,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":10,"content":"1月1日，我要在知乎直播倒背圆周率！你没有看错，我要倒着背。我相信这一定是继哥德巴赫猜想被证明后2019年第二大的数学事件！来看我直播吧。","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560454605,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"753d8d93574591c259941bfe7a0daa8b","url_token":"jiang-huai-82","name":"予淮","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-9d4a4cbaa62039c91a571c10376d6073_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-9d4a4cbaa62039c91a571c10376d6073_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/753d8d93574591c259941bfe7a0daa8b","user_type":"people","headline":"愿凭清风，愿以盛放。","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560454605","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545839027,"updated_time":1545839117,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"content":"\u003cp\u003e无论如何 结果无论对错 都很厉害了吧\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e至少比一些只知道冷嘲热讽的人不知道强了多少倍 这个问题下有温情 更多是看热闹的冷漠吧 事不关己 就可以随便践踏别人的自尊了吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个高中生 只知道初等数论 却敢去尝试这么难的数学猜想 这不是我们所提倡的事情吗 一个社会 如果没有这样的人涌现 反而有一堆人在一旁拼了命地把人从探索的路上拉回去 不是件特别可悲的事情吗\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我不是说他一定对 我数学不好 对数学好的人我一直抱着敬佩又仰慕的态度 我也不赞成这个问题的问法 真的证明出来 清北留不住你 但是下面一堆人的否定和嘲讽真的特别让人寒心  难道一个高中生的梦想就要受到这类无情的抨击 各类数学大神可以来帮忙纠正 但是怎么也轮不到对数论一窍不通 就等着数学大神证明正误后扑上来嘲笑的人批判\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e希望每个闪闪发光的梦想都能得到尊重\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e题主加油❤\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e以上。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560673220,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c17a2fa8908b8dfc9b80fc3170d4d13e","url_token":"zhi-hao-yu","name":"支浩宇","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/c17a2fa8908b8dfc9b80fc3170d4d13e","user_type":"people","headline":"广州天河工作","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560673220","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545878467,"updated_time":1545878467,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":0,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不能，参见日本数学家望月新一，此人2012年8月宣称证明了ABC猜想，到现在六年过去了，数学界没有几个人能看懂他的证明，也无法确认他的证明是否正确。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e对于一个高中生来说，假定你的证明是正确的，且能在6年时间内被数学界承认 — 这六年时间足够你读另一所大学读到大四了，更何况6年的时间还不一定足够。历史上很多科学发现是在发现者去世后才得到承认的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以，有好好的正常高考上大学的路你不走，非要傻走一条不知道要等多少年才通的路？ 如果真的这么傻，那就算你上100个北大也只是高分低能的废物。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560595661,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b4401598308fa66885d8f8eea520482e","url_token":"lin-wu-yz","name":"二十四节器","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8f50e5cbd67ca0a982dac9997ae6c7f3_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8f50e5cbd67ca0a982dac9997ae6c7f3_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/b4401598308fa66885d8f8eea520482e","user_type":"people","headline":"仗节死义，大器晚成","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560595661